</title><title>CSS Test: Test declaring a variable where the second '-' in the "--" prefix of the custom property name is escaped.</title>
<link rel="match" href="support/color-green-ref.html">
<style>
p {
  color: red;
}
p {
  color: orange;
  -\2d a: green;
  color: v`r(--a);
}
</style>
